262
00:25:01.166 --> 00:25:03.794
- Aegon the conqueror.
- To aegon.

263
00:25:07.006 --> 00:25:08.886
This brings me to some business.

264
00:25:09.633 --> 00:25:11.802
A proposal I wish to make

265
00:25:11.885 --> 00:25:14.805
in the spirit of honoring
our storied alliance.

266
00:25:14.888 --> 00:25:17.349
If your aim is to marry
one of our daughters. your excellence.

267
00:25:17.433 --> 00:25:19.536
you might have said so
and spared us the history lesson.

268
00:25:19.560 --> 00:25:20.880
What?

269
00:25:21.854 --> 00:25:25.024
I would not count myself
so deserving. my lady laena.

270
00:25:27.651 --> 00:25:32.031
I wish to offer you
a permanent residence here in pentos.

271
00:25:32.114 --> 00:25:34.533
This manse I would gift
to you. outright.

272
00:25:34.616 --> 00:25:36.910
along with its farms and lands.

273
00:25:36.994 --> 00:25:38.704
the vineyard and the wood.

274
00:25:38.787 --> 00:25:40.914
The tenants would pay
their tributes annually

275
00:25:40.998 --> 00:25:42.875
to their new Targaryen lord.

276
00:25:42.958 --> 00:25:45.711
You would have your freedom
of the city and the harbor.

277
00:25:45.794 --> 00:25:48.589
as befits your royal station.

278
00:25:51.759 --> 00:25:53.135
Continue.

279
00:25:53.218 --> 00:25:56.513
Lys and its allies rise again.

280
00:25:56.597 --> 00:26:00.726
The triarchy has made common cause
with qoren martell of dorne.

281
00:26:01.226 --> 00:26:04.271
At any moment.
they may turn their sights north.

282
00:26:04.354 --> 00:26:06.774
Your family has dragons.

283
00:26:06.857 --> 00:26:10.694
Three now. mayhaps four in the future.

284
00:26:11.695 --> 00:26:15.532
My aim is to protect pentos
from the lustful eye of the triarchy.

285
00:26:15.616 --> 00:26:19.328
Aid pentos in this. as aegon once did...

286
00:26:19.953 --> 00:26:24.124
And my gratitude will fill your cup
and overflow it.

287
00:26:24.208 --> 00:26:26.502
Your excellence. we are travelers.

288
00:26:26.585 --> 00:26:29.213
We've already extended our visit here.

289
00:26:33.592 --> 00:26:35.385
It's a most generous offer.

290
00:26:36.053 --> 00:26:38.055
And one we will certainly entertain.

291
00:27:08.544 --> 00:27:11.088
You are considering
prince reggio's offer.

292
00:27:11.171 --> 00:27:13.173
We have a good life here.

293
00:27:13.257 --> 00:27:16.552
We're free to do as we please.
welcomed and feted.

294
00:27:16.635 --> 00:27:19.054
- And eternally guests.
- Precisely.

295
00:27:19.138 --> 00:27:22.099
We are without responsibility.
The political scheming.

296
00:27:22.182 --> 00:27:24.852
the endless shifting
of loyalties and succession

297
00:27:24.935 --> 00:27:26.436
is none of ours.

298
00:27:27.187 --> 00:27:30.190
- They are using us.
- It's refreshing. isn't it?

299
00:27:31.650 --> 00:27:33.360
A simple transaction.

300
00:27:33.443 --> 00:27:35.946
We have dragons. they have gold.

301
00:27:41.160 --> 00:27:43.036
We are more than this. daemon.

302
00:27:43.120 --> 00:27:44.454
We are not minstrels or mummers

303
00:27:44.538 --> 00:27:46.182
who play at the pleasure
of an alien prince.

304
00:27:46.206 --> 00:27:48.625
We are the blood of old valyria.

305
00:27:49.626 --> 00:27:50.961
We don't belong here.

306
00:27:51.044 --> 00:27:53.463
Valyria is gone.
We don't belong anywhere.

307
00:27:59.595 --> 00:28:04.183
I want my child to be born
where I was born. on driftmark.

308
00:28:04.266 --> 00:28:05.434
in my lord father's castle.

309
00:28:05.517 --> 00:28:08.228
I want my daughters to be
raised in their homeland

310
00:28:08.312 --> 00:28:12.316
with their family
according to their birthright.

311
00:28:14.443 --> 00:28:17.905
And at my end. I want to die
a dragonrider's death.

312
00:28:17.988 --> 00:28:20.616
Not that of some fat country lord.

313
00:28:53.607 --> 00:28:55.776
Soften your knees.

314
00:28:55.859 --> 00:28:56.860
Feet light.

315
00:28:58.278 --> 00:29:00.006
Keep your feet light
and your hands heavy.

316
00:29:00.030 --> 00:29:02.574
This is the stuff. lyonel.

317
00:29:02.658 --> 00:29:06.078
Lads that learn together.
train together...

318
00:29:06.161 --> 00:29:09.039
Knock each other down.
pick each other up.

319
00:29:09.122 --> 00:29:11.875
They will certainly form
a lifelong bond. wouldn't you agree?

320
00:29:12.626 --> 00:29:14.086
That is the hope. your grace.

321
00:29:16.964 --> 00:29:19.549
Don't stand too upright. my prince.
You'll get knocked down.

322
00:29:30.727 --> 00:29:31.728
Aegon.

323
00:29:33.522 --> 00:29:35.291
I've won my first bout.
ser criston.

324
00:29:35.315 --> 00:29:37.734
My opponent sues for mercy.

325
00:29:38.277 --> 00:29:41.405
You'll have a new opponent then.
my lord of the straw.

326
00:29:41.488 --> 00:29:43.073
Let's see if you can touch me.

327
00:29:44.032 --> 00:29:45.450
You and your brother.

328
00:30:13.020 --> 00:30:14.646
You're gonna have
to do better than that.

329
00:30:19.109 --> 00:30:20.277
Ah!

330
00:30:20.360 --> 00:30:21.361
Weapons up. boys.

331
00:30:21.945 --> 00:30:23.572
Give your enemies no quarter.

332
00:30:25.907 --> 00:30:27.617
It seems the younger boys
could do better

333
00:30:27.701 --> 00:30:30.996
with a bit of your attention.
ser criston.

334
00:30:31.079 --> 00:30:33.999
You question my method
of instruction. ser?

335
00:30:34.082 --> 00:30:37.544
Oh. I merely suggest that
method be applied to all your pupils.

336
00:30:41.256 --> 00:30:42.257
Very well.

337
00:30:45.844 --> 00:30:47.846
Jacaerys. come here.

338
00:30:47.929 --> 00:30:49.139
You spar with aegon.

339
00:30:52.351 --> 00:30:53.769
Eldest son against eldest son.

340
00:30:57.022 --> 00:30:58.357
It's hardly a fair match.

341
00:30:58.440 --> 00:31:00.668
I know you've never seen true battle.
ser. but when steel is drawn.

342
00:31:00.692 --> 00:31:02.652
a fair match isn't something
anyone should expect.

343
00:31:05.405 --> 00:31:06.615
Blades up.

344
00:31:07.866 --> 00:31:08.950
Engage.

345
00:31:14.873 --> 00:31:15.873
Ah!

346
00:31:15.916 --> 00:31:18.126
[{Chuches]

347
00:31:33.350 --> 00:31:34.810
- Foul play.
- I'll deal with him.

348
00:31:37.896 --> 00:31:39.731
Plant your feet.
You have a height advantage.

349
00:31:39.815 --> 00:31:42.609
Use it. Advance on him...

350
00:31:46.988 --> 00:31:48.115
You!

351
00:31:49.616 --> 00:31:50.784
Close with him.

352
00:31:51.660 --> 00:31:53.912
Press him backward!
Close with him!

353
00:31:54.413 --> 00:31:56.415
Stay on the attack! Use your feet!

354
00:31:59.751 --> 00:32:00.752
Don't let him get up.

355
00:32:03.338 --> 00:32:04.589
Stay on the attack!

356
00:32:05.966 --> 00:32:07.175
Enough!

357
00:32:08.927 --> 00:32:11.555
- You dare put hands on me?
- Aegon!

358
00:32:11.638 --> 00:32:13.518
You forget yourself. strong.
That is the prince.

359
00:32:13.598 --> 00:32:15.225
This is what you teach. Cole?

360
00:32:17.769 --> 00:32:18.979
Cruelty...

361
00:32:19.980 --> 00:32:21.148
To the weaker opponent?

362
00:32:24.151 --> 00:32:25.920
Your interest
in the princeling's training

363
00:32:25.944 --> 00:32:27.362
is quite unusual. commander.

364
00:32:29.656 --> 00:32:31.491
Most men would only
have that kind of devotion

365
00:32:31.575 --> 00:32:32.993
toward a cousin...

366
00:32:34.744 --> 00:32:35.745
Or a brother...

367
00:32:36.830 --> 00:32:37.831
Or a $0”.

368
00:32:54.473 --> 00:32:56.099
Get back!

369
00:32:56.641 --> 00:32:58.101
Say it again!

370
00:32:58.935 --> 00:33:00.353
Say it again!

371
00:33:00.437 --> 00:33:02.189
Thought as much.

372
00:33:05.650 --> 00:33:07.290
Let him be bathed with a cloth.

373
00:33:07.319 --> 00:33:08.904
and see to it the cook

374
00:33:08.987 --> 00:33:10.989
gives you a good. clear wine to drink.

375
00:33:13.492 --> 00:33:14.576
Princess...

376
00:33:15.410 --> 00:33:18.622
There's been an incident in the yard.

377
00:33:28.006 --> 00:33:30.258
It fills me
with unrelenting shame.

378
00:33:30.342 --> 00:33:32.677
So that's what
this is about then?

379
00:33:32.761 --> 00:33:35.388
- Your shame?
- Our shame. han/vin!

380
00:33:36.348 --> 00:33:37.891
Shame on the whole of house strong.

381
00:33:37.974 --> 00:33:40.852
Because I laid my hands
on that insufferable Cole.

382
00:33:40.936 --> 00:33:41.853
the son of a steward?

383
00:33:41.937 --> 00:33:43.372
He is a knight
of the kingsguard now.

384
00:33:43.396 --> 00:33:45.291
- a defender of the crown.
- He assailed prince jacaerys.

385
00:33:45.315 --> 00:33:47.150
the future heir to the throne.

386
00:33:49.194 --> 00:33:53.365
You have laid us open to accusations

387
00:33:53.448 --> 00:33:55.200
of an uglier treachery.

388
00:33:55.283 --> 00:33:57.452
And what treachery is that?

389
00:33:59.955 --> 00:34:02.165
Don't play the fool with me. boy.

390
00:34:03.708 --> 00:34:06.878
Your intimacy with the Princess rhaenyra

391
00:34:06.962 --> 00:34:09.923
is an offense that would
mean exile and death...

392
00:34:10.465 --> 00:34:14.094
For you. for her. for the children!

393
00:34:15.178 --> 00:34:17.347
It is rumor only...

394
00:34:19.474 --> 00:34:20.850
Spun by the Princess's rivals.

395
00:34:20.934 --> 00:34:22.519
People have eyes. boy.

396
00:34:25.397 --> 00:34:29.693
Yet his grace the king. it seems.
will not accept what his eyes see.

397
00:34:29.776 --> 00:34:34.364
This flimsy shield alone
stands between you and the headsman.

398
00:34:35.490 --> 00:34:38.535
The willful blindness of a father
towards his child.

399
00:34:38.618 --> 00:34:41.079
I wish my father affected
a similar blindness.

400
00:34:41.162 --> 00:34:43.456
Have I not these many years?

401
00:34:44.082 --> 00:34:46.251
And yet today. you publicly assaulted

402
00:34:46.334 --> 00:34:49.337
a knight of the kingsguard
in the... in the defense of your...

403
00:34:52.173 --> 00:34:55.385
You have your honor
and I have mine.

404
00:35:03.518 --> 00:35:05.520
To ease the pain. Princess.

405
00:35:17.907 --> 00:35:20.577
- Thank you.
- You'll feel better in a day or two.

406
00:35:20.660 --> 00:35:22.287
when the milk dries up.

407
00:35:40.889 --> 00:35:42.891
My dear wife.

408
00:35:42.974 --> 00:35:44.809
Princess.

409
00:35:46.645 --> 00:35:47.854
I fell down.

410
00:35:50.106 --> 00:35:52.275
- Where have you been?
- Out with qarl.

411
00:35:52.359 --> 00:35:53.359
Didn't I mention it?

412
00:35:55.236 --> 00:35:57.530
Are you in very much pain?

413
00:35:57.614 --> 00:35:58.615
The milk...

414
00:35:59.866 --> 00:36:02.118
- Swells the breasts...
- Would you mind. ser qarl?

415
00:36:02.202 --> 00:36:03.787
I would like to speak with my husband.

416
00:36:03.870 --> 00:36:05.580
Of course. Princess.

417
00:36:17.050 --> 00:36:21.179
War is afoot again
in the stepstones. rhaenyra.

418
00:36:22.013 --> 00:36:26.476
The triarchy takes new life
from its alliance with dorne.

419
00:36:27.560 --> 00:36:29.562
They're waylaying ships and cargo.

420
00:36:30.188 --> 00:36:32.857
Qarl's been fighting there.
He showed me a...

421
00:36:36.111 --> 00:36:39.906
He showed me a sack of sapphires
big as walnuts

422
00:36:39.989 --> 00:36:41.991
he took from the pirate he slew.

423
00:36:44.536 --> 00:36:47.831
After all this time.
this is just what I need.

424
00:36:47.914 --> 00:36:49.582
a little adventure.

425
00:36:49.666 --> 00:36:53.086
A good. honest battle
to enliven my blood again.

426
00:36:54.379 --> 00:36:56.965
He says there is
a tyroshi general there.

427
00:36:57.048 --> 00:36:58.800
a giant. they say.

428
00:36:58.883 --> 00:37:03.513
who dyes his beard purple
and wears women's frocks.

429
00:37:07.350 --> 00:37:09.310
A few months. maybe...

430
00:37:13.982 --> 00:37:15.942
To be back at sea.

431
00:37:17.902 --> 00:37:19.821
Are you mad?

432
00:37:20.739 --> 00:37:22.157
Do you know what's happened...

433
00:37:23.450 --> 00:37:25.553
While you've been guzzling all the ale
in flea bottom?

434
00:37:25.577 --> 00:37:27.203
Gods know what besides?

435
00:37:28.246 --> 00:37:30.540
Dark rumors are hunting us. laenor.

436
00:37:30.623 --> 00:37:32.709
They nip at our heels.

437
00:37:32.792 --> 00:37:37.672
Questions about our sons' parentage.

438
00:37:38.590 --> 00:37:40.884
Vile. disgusting insinuations.

439
00:37:41.968 --> 00:37:43.595
Insinuations. are they?

440
00:37:44.095 --> 00:37:46.055
They are our sons!

441
00:37:46.139 --> 00:37:48.141
Yours and mine.

442
00:37:49.017 --> 00:37:51.227
And their true father
will not abandon them now

443
00:37:51.311 --> 00:37:54.731
to go carousing through the narrow sea.
waggling his sword

444
00:37:54.814 --> 00:37:57.192
- and winking at his sailors.
- I am a knight...

445
00:37:59.527 --> 00:38:00.528
And a warrior.

446
00:38:01.780 --> 00:38:06.743
And I have played
my part here. faithfully...

447
00:38:07.994 --> 00:38:10.997
For ten years.

448
00:38:12.165 --> 00:38:15.001
- I am owed some...
- You are owed nothing!

449
00:38:16.211 --> 00:38:21.174
For ten years. you have indulged
yourself at court.

450
00:38:21.257 --> 00:38:23.718
bought the finest horses.

451
00:38:23.802 --> 00:38:26.221
drunk the rarest of wines.

452
00:38:26.304 --> 00:38:27.931
fucked the lustiest boys.

453
00:38:28.014 --> 00:38:31.434
This was our agreement.
I have not begrudged you.

454
00:38:32.310 --> 00:38:33.394
But...

455
00:38:35.063 --> 00:38:39.317
You do not desert your post
when the storm lashes.

456
00:38:39.400 --> 00:38:44.030
The wise sailor
flees the storm as it gathers.

457
00:38:54.415 --> 00:38:56.668
Very well then. I command you.

458
00:38:58.127 --> 00:39:00.046
As your Princess
and the heir to the throne.

459
00:39:00.129 --> 00:39:02.215
you are commanded

460
00:39:02.298 --> 00:39:05.677
to remain in king's landing
and at my side.

461
00:39:26.281 --> 00:39:28.283
It's been eight years. sweetling.

462
00:39:29.826 --> 00:39:32.745
- Half of them never do. you know?
- What?

463
00:39:35.707 --> 00:39:36.708
Hatch.

464
00:39:39.794 --> 00:39:41.421
Will they let me stay?

465
00:39:42.755 --> 00:39:44.382
Will who let you stay?

466
00:39:44.924 --> 00:39:46.551
The prince of pentos.

467
00:39:47.635 --> 00:39:49.262
I don't understand.

468
00:39:50.388 --> 00:39:52.390
He wants you and father...

469
00:39:53.766 --> 00:39:55.184
And baela...

470
00:39:55.768 --> 00:39:57.604
'Cause you have dragons.

471
00:40:02.066 --> 00:40:05.737
There is more than one way
to bind yourself to a dragon.

472
00:40:05.820 --> 00:40:10.450
I was without one
until I was 15 years old

473
00:40:10.533 --> 00:40:14.746
and now I ride vhagar.
the largest in the world.

474
00:40:18.082 --> 00:40:19.918
You have a harder road.

475
00:40:20.001 --> 00:40:21.961
Baela's dragon was born to her.

476
00:40:24.505 --> 00:40:26.049
But if you wish to be a rider.

477
00:40:26.132 --> 00:40:29.135
you must claim that right.

478
00:40:30.762 --> 00:40:32.764
Your father would tell you the same.

479
00:40:34.265 --> 00:40:35.642
Father ignores me.

480
00:40:42.607 --> 00:40:44.108
He's doing his best.

481
00:41:22.271 --> 00:41:24.273
Laenor has written.

482
00:41:25.650 --> 00:41:27.819
Rhaenyra has delivered another son.

483
00:41:30.238 --> 00:41:31.823
Does your brother mention if this one

484
00:41:31.906 --> 00:41:34.450
also bears a marked
but entirely coincidental

485
00:41:34.534 --> 00:41:37.161
resemblance to the commander
of the city watch?

486
00:41:38.329 --> 00:41:40.623
He seems to have left that detail out.

487
00:41:40.707 --> 00:41:41.708
Mmm.

488
00:41:43.584 --> 00:41:45.712
I miss my brother. daemon.

489
00:41:48.214 --> 00:41:49.465
As I think do you.

490
00:41:51.592 --> 00:41:53.803
I miss westerosi strongwine.

491
00:41:55.513 --> 00:41:58.224
It could be depended on for a few hours
of peaceful oblivion.

492
00:42:00.351 --> 00:42:02.770
This Amber shit that they drink here.

493
00:42:10.570 --> 00:42:12.613
Do you never long for home?

494
00:42:14.198 --> 00:42:16.784
- I don't believe you.
- Believe what you please.

495
00:42:16.868 --> 00:42:20.955
You laud the virtues of pentos.
but you have no interest in it.

496
00:42:21.039 --> 00:42:23.624
If you did. you would venture
into the city. but instead.

497
00:42:23.708 --> 00:42:27.170
you spend your time here.
in the library. reading accounts

498
00:42:27.253 --> 00:42:30.548
of the same dead dragonlords
whose legacy you claim

499
00:42:30.631 --> 00:42:32.091
has no hold on you.

500
00:42:32.175 --> 00:42:34.635
Didn't know I was being
so minutely observed.

501
00:42:34.719 --> 00:42:36.179
You do not sleep.

502
00:42:36.262 --> 00:42:38.806
Well. how can I with you
haunting my every move?

503
00:42:42.226 --> 00:42:44.666
Life has. I know. disappointed you.

504
00:42:45.521 --> 00:42:48.149
Perhaps. I too. am not the wife
you would've wished for yourself.

505
00:42:48.232 --> 00:42:49.442
Laena.

506
00:42:49.525 --> 00:42:50.985
It does not pain me.

507
00:42:52.320 --> 00:42:53.863
I have made my peace.

508
00:42:58.159 --> 00:42:59.786
But you are more than this. daemon.

509
00:43:02.246 --> 00:43:05.208
The man I married was more than this.

510
00:43:12.965 --> 00:43:15.301
It is lord blackwood's
contention. therefore.

511
00:43:15.384 --> 00:43:17.064
that the brackens moved
the boundary stones

512
00:43:17.095 --> 00:43:18.429
in the dead of the night

513
00:43:18.513 --> 00:43:20.973
and put their horses
to graze in his field.

514
00:43:21.057 --> 00:43:23.601
Why was this issue not
brought before lord grover?

515
00:43:23.684 --> 00:43:26.813
Has he grown so feeble
he cannot settle a quarrel over rocks?

516
00:43:26.896 --> 00:43:31.275
I've heard tale that lord grover's son
now rules riverrun in all but name.

517
00:43:31.359 --> 00:43:35.655
Well. he is also a Tully
and this remains a Tully problem.

518
00:43:35.738 --> 00:43:36.906
I would agree.

519
00:43:37.949 --> 00:43:40.368
- If we may move on. my lords...
- And yet.

520
00:43:40.451 --> 00:43:41.911
the brackens and the blackwoods

521
00:43:41.994 --> 00:43:44.038
will use any excuse
to spill each other's blood.

522
00:43:47.291 --> 00:43:50.586
So this dispute bears looking into.

523
00:43:50.670 --> 00:43:52.088
There will be countryfolk who know

524
00:43:52.171 --> 00:43:54.549
where the lines have
been drawn for generations.

525
00:43:54.632 --> 00:43:55.925
That is easy enough.

526
00:43:57.093 --> 00:43:58.553
Of course.

527
00:44:00.805 --> 00:44:01.931
Ser tyland.

528
00:44:03.057 --> 00:44:05.434
Um. we should address

529
00:44:05.518 --> 00:44:08.396
the latest developments
in the stepstones. my lords.

530
00:44:08.479 --> 00:44:11.107
Will we ever be shut
of that blasted place?

531
00:44:11.190 --> 00:44:12.984
If you ask me.
I think the blackwoods have

532
00:44:13.067 --> 00:44:14.569
- the upper hand.
- No.

533
00:44:14.652 --> 00:44:17.029
We've moved on to the stepstones.
lord beesbury.

534
00:44:17.113 --> 00:44:20.575
And the triarchy's
new alliance with dorne.

535
00:44:20.658 --> 00:44:22.994
I was hoping
our negotiations with sunspear

536
00:44:23.077 --> 00:44:24.579
might persuade
them to see reason.

537
00:44:26.497 --> 00:44:29.375
To trust a martell
is to be disappointed.

538
00:44:29.458 --> 00:44:31.961
And where. I wonder.
is our prince daemon?

539
00:44:32.044 --> 00:44:34.505
Or I suppose I should call him king.
as he styled himself

540
00:44:34.589 --> 00:44:37.216
when he won a battle there... once.

541
00:44:37.300 --> 00:44:40.052
That was a decade ago and he has
since left the region undefended.

542
00:44:40.136 --> 00:44:41.905
We have left it undefended.

543
00:44:41.929 --> 00:44:44.891
There should've been
fortifications built.

544
00:44:44.974 --> 00:44:46.809
watchtowers. a fleet of ships.

545
00:44:46.893 --> 00:44:49.604
a Garrison of soldiers
sent to hold our ground.

546
00:44:49.687 --> 00:44:50.897
We cannot afford it.

547
00:44:53.149 --> 00:44:56.485
Our coffers are great. but not infinite.

548
00:44:57.153 --> 00:44:59.155
We must consider
the cost to our subjects.

549
00:44:59.238 --> 00:45:02.241
- I must agree.
- The cost of war is greater.

550
00:45:04.619 --> 00:45:08.831
But we have been lax
and the old monster now lifts its head.

551
00:45:14.086 --> 00:45:15.254
Let us be finished.

552
00:45:16.839 --> 00:45:18.257
Yes.

553
00:45:22.303 --> 00:45:23.304
Wait.

554
00:45:24.347 --> 00:45:25.473
I wish to speak.

555
00:45:27.225 --> 00:45:28.226
Be seated.

556
00:45:37.693 --> 00:45:40.655
I have felt the...

557
00:45:41.822 --> 00:45:43.115
Strife...

558
00:45:44.075 --> 00:45:46.452
Between our families of late. my queen.

559
00:45:49.121 --> 00:45:52.959
And for any offense given by mine.
I apologize.

560
00:45:55.044 --> 00:45:57.255
But we are one house.

561
00:45:58.297 --> 00:46:00.800
And long before that.

562
00:46:00.883 --> 00:46:02.301
we were friends.

563
00:46:08.432 --> 00:46:11.185
My son jacaerys will inherit
the iron throne after me.

564
00:46:11.269 --> 00:46:13.938
I propose we betroth him
to your daughter. helaena.

565
00:46:15.815 --> 00:46:17.817
Ally ourselves...

566
00:46:18.442 --> 00:46:20.319
Once and for all.

567
00:46:20.903 --> 00:46:22.613
Let them rule together.

568
00:46:22.697 --> 00:46:24.699
A mostjudicious proposition.

569
00:46:29.745 --> 00:46:33.291
Additionally. if syrax brings forth
another clutch of eggs.

570
00:46:33.374 --> 00:46:35.835
your son aemond will have
his choice of them. uh...

571
00:46:37.086 --> 00:46:39.714
A symbol of our goodwill.

572
00:46:42.717 --> 00:46:44.093
Rhaenyra...

573
00:46:51.934 --> 00:46:54.562
Oh. seven hells. Um...

574
00:46:56.814 --> 00:46:58.441
My dear...

575
00:46:58.524 --> 00:47:00.943
A dragon's egg is a handsome gift.

576
00:47:02.570 --> 00:47:06.157
The king and I thank you for your offer
and we will consider it duly.

577
00:47:06.240 --> 00:47:08.242
You must rest now. husband.

578
00:47:11.454 --> 00:47:12.830
Yes.

579
00:47:19.170 --> 00:47:22.965
How sweetly the fox speaks
when it's been cornered by the hounds.

580
00:47:23.049 --> 00:47:26.093
- She is sincere.
- She is desperate.

581
00:47:26.177 --> 00:47:28.387
She feels the earth
washing away beneath her feet

582
00:47:28.471 --> 00:47:30.806
and now she expects us
to ignore her transgressions

583
00:47:30.890 --> 00:47:34.143
and for me to marry my only daughter
to one of her...

584
00:47:34.226 --> 00:47:35.978
Plain-featured sons.

585
00:47:36.062 --> 00:47:38.689
The proposal is a good one. my queen.

586
00:47:39.732 --> 00:47:41.317
We're a family.

587
00:47:41.400 --> 00:47:43.736
Let us put aside
these childish quarrels.

588
00:47:43.819 --> 00:47:46.238
Join hands and be stronger for it.

589
00:47:47.365 --> 00:47:49.367
You may do as you wish. husband...

590
00:47:50.368 --> 00:47:52.787
When I am cold in my grave.

591
00:47:53.537 --> 00:47:54.538
Alicent.

592
00:47:56.582 --> 00:47:57.666
Alicent!

593
00:48:21.273 --> 00:48:23.275
I do not need the blanket...

594
00:48:26.779 --> 00:48:28.406
The hand. your grace.

595
00:48:29.031 --> 00:48:32.034
- The king is resting.
- I will see him.

596
00:48:33.202 --> 00:48:34.412
Lean fonnard.

597
00:48:41.836 --> 00:48:44.672
I'm being endlessly fussed over. lyonel.

598
00:48:45.381 --> 00:48:48.008
It's a wonder
I can visit the privy alone.

599
00:48:48.759 --> 00:48:49.760
Your grace.

600
00:48:50.928 --> 00:48:52.972
What might this errand
be about. lord lyonel?

601
00:48:55.850 --> 00:48:57.184
Your grace. I feel...

602
00:48:59.812 --> 00:49:02.398
I have come to resign my position
as hand of the king.

603
00:49:04.024 --> 00:49:05.693
The episode in the yard this morning.

604
00:49:05.776 --> 00:49:08.821
My son hannin has disgraced himself

605
00:49:08.904 --> 00:49:11.866
and every fishwife in king's landing
will soon be telling the tale.

606
00:49:11.949 --> 00:49:16.120
Young hannin's outburst was unfortunate.
it's true.

607
00:49:16.203 --> 00:49:17.913
But he's been expelled
from the city watch.

608
00:49:17.997 --> 00:49:19.373
That seems punishment enough.

609
00:49:19.457 --> 00:49:21.041
Forgive me. your grace. it is not.

610
00:49:28.966 --> 00:49:33.137
You have served me
faithfully for many years.

611
00:49:33.220 --> 00:49:34.472
ten as hand.

612
00:49:36.056 --> 00:49:40.227
Your advice has been sage.
unmarked by self-interest...

613
00:49:40.936 --> 00:49:43.689
Which stands in contrast to all others.

614
00:49:44.982 --> 00:49:46.567
You speak kind words...

615
00:49:47.860 --> 00:49:49.862
But there is a shadow over my house

616
00:49:49.945 --> 00:49:52.156
and it grows ever darker.

617
00:49:52.239 --> 00:49:54.867
I can no longer serve you
with integrity.

618
00:49:56.285 --> 00:49:57.369
What is this shadow?

619
00:49:59.246 --> 00:50:01.624
Name it. if it casts such a gloom.

620
00:50:01.707 --> 00:50:06.337
Yes. we must have your reasoning
in plain language.

621
00:50:14.220 --> 00:50:15.221
Icannot

622
00:50:17.473 --> 00:50:19.058
then I cannot accept this.

623
00:50:19.141 --> 00:50:21.143
- My dear husband...
- I said no!

624
00:50:22.478 --> 00:50:25.105
- If you insist. my king.
- I do.

625
00:50:26.023 --> 00:50:28.067
You will continue in your service
to the crown.

626
00:50:30.736 --> 00:50:32.780
I would then ask leave
to take my son from court

627
00:50:32.863 --> 00:50:35.950
and escort him back to the family seat
at harrenhal.

628
00:50:36.033 --> 00:50:38.035
He is my heir

629
00:50:38.118 --> 00:50:39.912
and will be lord of harren's castle
one day.

630
00:50:39.995 --> 00:50:42.623
It is time he assumed his duties there.

631
00:50:45.709 --> 00:50:46.794
Do it.

632
00:51:07.606 --> 00:51:09.608
Aren't you gonna help me?

633
00:51:49.064 --> 00:51:51.900
I took the Liberty of beginning
without you. your grace.

634
00:51:51.984 --> 00:51:54.737
It seemed a sin to let
such a pie grow cold.

635
00:51:54.820 --> 00:51:57.698
You did wisely. lord larys.

636
00:51:57.781 --> 00:52:00.618
Though you had no such worry
about the wine. surely.

637
00:52:00.701 --> 00:52:03.329
Meat without wine is also a sin.

638
00:52:03.412 --> 00:52:04.663
Hmm.

639
00:52:08.959 --> 00:52:11.587
It's been my duty to tell you
of happenings about the castle.

640
00:52:11.670 --> 00:52:14.673
but tonight you know. and I do not.

641
00:52:15.549 --> 00:52:18.302
The king had an audience with my father.

642
00:52:18.385 --> 00:52:19.928
He attempted to resign his post.

643
00:52:21.013 --> 00:52:22.139
I thought as much.

644
00:52:23.599 --> 00:52:27.227
His honor's always been a millstone
about his esteemed neck.

645
00:52:29.396 --> 00:52:31.357
Interesting you said "attempted"?

646
00:52:31.440 --> 00:52:33.442
My lord husband refused to accept.

647
00:52:34.693 --> 00:52:38.656
Then he fell short of confessing
my brother's... transgressions.

648
00:52:38.739 --> 00:52:40.949
With his eruption in the yard.
your brother

649
00:52:41.033 --> 00:52:43.160
all but confessed the truth himself.

650
00:52:43.243 --> 00:52:45.454
Truth has many flavors. your grace.

651
00:52:46.538 --> 00:52:49.208
Do you expect the king to doom
his dear daughter to exile.

652
00:52:49.291 --> 00:52:51.126
or even...

653
00:52:52.711 --> 00:52:53.921
Talya. not now.

654
00:53:01.220 --> 00:53:04.807
It's a willful blindness. the king.

655
00:53:04.890 --> 00:53:06.618
I mean. you'd surely
suffer the same affliction.

656
00:53:06.642 --> 00:53:08.560
- if it came to it.
- I would not.

657
00:53:10.396 --> 00:53:13.273
Lord lyonel is to escort
ser hannin back to harrenhal

658
00:53:13.357 --> 00:53:16.777
to watch over his seat
whilst he continues to serve as hand.

659
00:53:17.361 --> 00:53:22.074
But the hand is compromised
by the acts of his son.

660
00:53:22.157 --> 00:53:27.121
My father cannot give
unbiased counsel to the king.

661
00:53:27.204 --> 00:53:30.499
It is now that I most rue
the absence of my own father.

662
00:53:30.582 --> 00:53:32.519
He wouldn't hesitate
to speak the truth to the king.

663
00:53:32.543 --> 00:53:34.086
If Otto hightower were still hand...

664
00:53:34.169 --> 00:53:36.588
You cannot say. my queen.
that your father would be

665
00:53:36.672 --> 00:53:38.215
impartial in this matter.

666
00:53:38.298 --> 00:53:40.509
No. but he would be partial to me!

667
00:53:49.935 --> 00:53:52.938
In all of king's landing.
is there no one to take my side?

668
00:54:19.089 --> 00:54:22.301
What a collection of heroes
I have before me.

669
00:54:26.263 --> 00:54:28.015
A murderer...

670
00:54:28.599 --> 00:54:30.684
A deviant...

671
00:54:31.185 --> 00:54:33.187
A traitor to the crown.

672
00:54:33.896 --> 00:54:38.108
For your crimes. you've been sentenced
to death by hanging.

673
00:54:40.027 --> 00:54:42.029
What do you want with us?

674
00:54:45.199 --> 00:54:48.202
I am prepared to offer you mercy...

675
00:54:49.828 --> 00:54:52.831
If you're prepared
to pay a little price.

676
00:55:16.939 --> 00:55:18.666
Push. my lady.

677
00:55:18.690 --> 00:55:21.276
Push! Push!

678
00:55:22.152 --> 00:55:23.320
Push!

679
00:55:23.403 --> 00:55:25.948
- You must push!
- Push!

680
00:55:27.908 --> 00:55:30.160
It needs to come now!

681
00:55:30.244 --> 00:55:31.453
Push!

682
00:55:33.497 --> 00:55:35.123
Push!

683
00:55:35.833 --> 00:55:38.001
You must push now. my lady!

684
00:55:39.086 --> 00:55:40.504
Push!

685
00:55:58.856 --> 00:56:00.858
I've reached the limit of my art.

686
00:56:02.734 --> 00:56:04.361
The child will not come.

687
00:56:07.114 --> 00:56:09.116
Ah. my brave girl.

688
00:56:14.580 --> 00:56:16.060
I am very sorry. my prince.

689
00:56:17.958 --> 00:56:19.960
We could lay open the womb...

690
00:56:20.961 --> 00:56:23.171
Try to remove the infant

691
00:56:23.255 --> 00:56:24.882
by way of the blade.

692
00:56:26.133 --> 00:56:29.177
But I cannot say
for a surety whether it lives.

693
00:56:29.261 --> 00:56:30.721
Would the mother survive it?

694
00:57:05.047 --> 00:57:07.257
Vhagar. dracarys.

695
00:57:12.596 --> 00:57:13.764
Dracarys!

696
00:57:16.433 --> 00:57:17.851
Dracarys!

697
00:57:22.439 --> 00:57:24.024
Dracarys.

698
00:57:24.816 --> 00:57:26.818
Dracarys!

699
00:57:28.946 --> 00:57:30.530
Dracarys.

700
00:57:51.093 --> 00:57:52.302
Laena!

701
00:58:15.242 --> 00:58:17.162
Be good to your mother. lads.

702
00:58:17.494 --> 00:58:19.121
I'll visit when I can.

703
00:58:22.582 --> 00:58:24.042
But that may be some time.

704
00:58:27.921 --> 00:58:28.922
Jace.

705
00:58:35.971 --> 00:58:37.389
I will return...

706
00:58:40.058 --> 00:58:41.476
I promise.

707
00:58:56.324 --> 00:59:00.287
I will be a stranger when we meet again.

708
00:59:17.179 --> 00:59:18.180
Princess.

709
00:59:40.577 --> 00:59:43.288
We will exchange letters by raven.

710
00:59:43.371 --> 00:59:47.000
- Won't that be fun?
- Is hannin strong my father?

711
00:59:51.171 --> 00:59:52.547
Am I a bastard?

712
00:59:57.385 --> 00:59:58.929
You are a Targaryen.

713
01:00:00.931 --> 01:00:02.099
That's all that matters.

714
01:00:27.040 --> 01:00:28.083
A word?

715
01:00:35.090 --> 01:00:36.424
I take it he's gone.

716
01:00:39.010 --> 01:00:40.720
We're finished here. We're leaving.

717
01:00:43.723 --> 01:00:46.601
What of your offer? Jace and helaena?

718
01:00:46.685 --> 01:00:48.436
I have been undermined...

719
01:00:49.312 --> 01:00:52.524
And made a spectacle.
They whisper about me in the corridors.

720
01:00:52.607 --> 01:00:54.985
Well. I leave them to it.

721
01:00:58.947 --> 01:01:00.115
To dragonstone then?

722
01:01:01.158 --> 01:01:02.409
We should've left years ago.

723
01:01:08.665 --> 01:01:10.458
What of your position?

724
01:01:10.542 --> 01:01:12.878
You've always said
if you were absent from court.

725
01:01:12.961 --> 01:01:15.881
she would pour her honey
in your father's ear.

726
01:01:16.548 --> 01:01:19.718
The wise sailor
flees the storm as it gathers.

727
01:01:21.970 --> 01:01:23.388
Laenor...

728
01:01:25.140 --> 01:01:26.391
Bring him.

729
01:01:28.185 --> 01:01:30.312
We'll need every sword we can muster.

730
01:02:46.846 --> 01:02:50.267
Fire! I will burn!

731
01:02:50.350 --> 01:02:53.061
Hannin! Hannin!

732
01:03:17.502 --> 01:03:21.131
What are children.
but a weakness?

733
01:03:24.676 --> 01:03:26.303
A folly?

734
01:03:27.470 --> 01:03:29.306
A futility?

735
01:03:34.519 --> 01:03:36.688
Through them. you imagine you cheat

736
01:03:36.771 --> 01:03:39.983
the great darkness of its victory.

737
01:03:55.123 --> 01:04:00.128
You will persist forever.
in some form or another.

738
01:04:02.922 --> 01:04:06.092
As if they will keep you
from the dust.

739
01:04:17.145 --> 01:04:21.816
But for them.
you surrender what you should not.

740
01:04:24.611 --> 01:04:28.406
You may know what is
the right thing to be done.

741
01:04:28.490 --> 01:04:31.868
but love stays the hand.

742
01:04:40.794 --> 01:04:42.003
Love...

743
01:04:44.130 --> 01:04:46.132
Is a downfall.

744
01:04:51.096 --> 01:04:54.599
Best to make your way
through life unencumbered...

745
01:04:56.184 --> 01:04:57.644
If you ask me.

746
01:05:01.314 --> 01:05:02.607
They're dead.

747
01:05:02.690 --> 01:05:05.693
You've heard the stories
of harrenhal. your grace.

748
01:05:07.404 --> 01:05:09.447
It was built in hubris
by harren the black

749
01:05:09.531 --> 01:05:11.908
as a monument to his own greatness.

750
01:05:11.991 --> 01:05:14.994
Blood mixed into the mortar.

751
01:05:17.163 --> 01:05:19.624
It is said to be a cursed place.

752
01:05:20.291 --> 01:05:24.087
That it passes judgment
on all who pass beneath its gates.

753
01:05:24.170 --> 01:05:25.797
You...

754
01:05:25.880 --> 01:05:27.882
You passed judgment.

755
01:05:29.509 --> 01:05:30.885
The queen makes a wish.

756
01:05:32.804 --> 01:05:36.474
What servant of the realm
would not strive to fulfill it?

757
01:05:38.435 --> 01:05:42.063
I assume you will write
to your father now?

758
01:05:44.023 --> 01:05:45.024
Larys...

759
01:05:46.192 --> 01:05:48.445
I did not wish for this.

760
01:05:50.655 --> 01:05:54.534
I feel certain you will reward me...

761
01:05:56.327 --> 01:05:58.663
When the time is right.

761
01:05:59.305 --> 01:06:59.925
